        </h1>

        <div class="tab">
            <input type="radio" name="acc" id="acc1">
            <label for="acc1">
                <h2>01</h2>
                <h3>What content can I find on the streaming platform?</h3>
            </label>
            <div class="content">
                <p>Our streaming platform offers a vast library of movies and TV shows. You can explore a wide range of content, including:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Latest movies</li>
                    <li>Popular TV series</li>
                    <li>Classic films</li>
                    <li>Original productions</li>
                    <li>Documentaries</li>
                </ul>
                <p>We cover various genres such as action, drama, comedy, sci-fi, and more. Whether you're a fan of classic movies or seeking the latest releases, you'll find something to watch on our platform.</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="tab">
            <input type="radio" name="acc" id="acc2">
            <label for="acc2">
                <h2>02</h2>
                <h3>Is everything available for free?</h3>
            </label>
            <div class="content">
                <p>No, not all content on our streaming platform is free. We offer a variety of content, including both free and premium options.
                    While many titles are accessible at no cost, some movies or TV shows may require a rental or purchase fee. Additionally, we offer subscription-based access to exclusive content and an ad-free experience.
                    When browsing our platform, you will encounter content with various access methods, including:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Free titles</li>
                    <li>Purchase options</li>
                    <li>Subscription-based access</li>
                </ul>
                <p>Before streaming a title, make sure to check its access method and any applicable terms and conditions.</p>
                <p>Enjoy your favorite movies and TV shows, whether they are free or part of a premium experience.</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="tab">
            <input type="radio" name="acc" id="acc3">
            <label for="acc3">
                <h2>03</h2>
                <h3>How can I start watching movies and TV shows on the platform?</h3>
            </label>
            <div class="content">
                <p>To start watching movies and TV shows on our platform, please follow these simple steps:</p>
                <ol>
                    <li>Visit our website and create an account.</li>
                    <li>Browse the catalog and select a movie or TV show you want to watch.</li>
                    <li>Depending on the content, choose to rent, purchase, or access for free.</li>
                    <li>Stream the selected title directly on your device.</li>
                    <li>Enjoy high-quality entertainment from the comfort of your home.</li>
                </ol>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="tab">
            <input type="radio" name="acc" id="acc4">
            <label for="acc4">
