                <h3>How do I receive updates about new releases?</h3>
            </label>
            <div class="content">
                <p>Stay up-to-date with the latest movie and TV show releases by following these steps:</p>
                <ol>
                    <li>Visit our website to find announcements and trailers for upcoming content.</li>
                    <li>Follow us on social media for real-time updates and exclusive content previews.</li>
                </ol>
                <p>Don't miss out on new releases and exciting updates in the world of entertainment.</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="tab">
            <input type="radio" name="acc" id="acc5">
            <label for="acc5">
                <h2>05</h2>
                <h3>How can I contact customer support?</h3>
            </label>
            <div class="content">
                <p>If you have questions or need assistance, our customer support team is here to help. You can contact us through the following methods:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Send an email to support@beestream.com</li>
                    <li>Visit our 'Contact Us' page on the website to submit a support request.</li>
                    <li>Call our toll-free support hotline at (+94) 112 076656.</li>
                </ul>
                <p>We're committed to providing you with the best streaming experience, so please don't hesitate to reach out.</p>
